Place oil, curry powder and onion in a small saucepan. Heat on medium high heat. Simmer 1-2 minutes or until onions are tender. Add lemon juice, SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener and salt. Simmer over medium heat approx. 1 minute or until sauce begins to thicken. Remove from heat and cool. Add mayonnaise to cooled sauce. Stir well. Place prepared salad ingredients in a large bowl. Toss with dressing until evenly coated. Serve on salad greens. Garnish with a sprinkling of chopped apricots.